> > >> refer to include/linux/stat.h defines to find out what mode it is
> > >> because numbers are actually quickier to understand.
> > >>
> > >> Compare and contrast:
> > >>
> > >>       0644 vs S_IRUGO|S_IWUSR vs rw_r__r__
